name: The Sad Letter
description:
This collage is part of a project called "Strange Visions" a series of photographs taken by Emil Nova between 2007 and 2013 using low-budget cameras in order to capture images spontaneously. Each collage tells a story and reflects on various aspects of life. For this project almost no editing tools were used.
Dimensions: 1920 x 1920 pixels
Twitter: @EmilNovaNFT
